The current Free Democratic Party ( FDP ) , which was the joint successor of the DVP and the social - liberal German Democratic Party ( DDP ) , originally featured conservative and partly nationalist efforts , which were particularly strong in some state associations until the 1950s and more occasionally after that ( an interesting example is that of Jürgen Möllemann , FDP leader in North Rhine - Westphalia in 1983–1994 and 1996–2002 ) , and still includes a national - liberal faction , which holds a consistently Eurosceptic position , differently from the rest of the party .
